edu.jhu.zpalmer2.spring2009.ai.hw6.shell

Class Shell

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.jhu.zpalmer2.spring2009.ai.hw6.shell.Shell

  • public class Shell
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the Reinforcement Learning Agent Shell (RLASH) which allows a user to issue commands to the system.

      • execute

        public void execute(java.lang.String[] initialCommands)
             throws java.io.IOException
        Executes this shell. This method will execute commands read from the provided input until termination is requested or the end of input is reached. Before executing commands read from standard input, it will execute the commands provided in the initalCommands parameter. These commands will be executed without displaying a prompt.
        Parameters:
        initialCommands - The commands to execute before displaying a prompt.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - If an I/O error occurs while reading input.
